    "shortDescription": "<p>A bank of fog billows out from the point you designate. The fog obscures all sight, including darkvision, beyond 5 feet. A creature within 5 feet has concealment (attacks have a 20% miss chance).</p><p>Creatures farther away have total concealment (50% miss chance, and the attacker can't use sight to locate the target).</p><p>A moderate wind (11+ mph) disperses the fog in 4 rounds; a strong wind (21+ mph) disperses the fog in 1 round.</p><p>The spell does not function underwater.</p>"
